instance dt_constellation : DTDFVocab:Constellation [
    base:desc "The architecture follows ISO 23247 Reference Architecture, mapping SW functional entities (FEs) onto individual ROS 2 packages that encapsulate ROS 2 nodes implementing the entity behaviours. The User Entity contains the User Interface FE split into two sub‑components (3D Visualization and Control Panel). The Digital Twin Entity hosts data‑management and control FEs, while the Physical Twin Entity incorporates data pre‑processing, actuation, and device‑communication FEs such as Point Cloud Clustering & Tracking. The orchestration is decentralized across hardware nodes, with resource management handled by ROS 2’s node lifecycle and package deployment on each hardware platform. System‑wide coordination is achieved via ROS 2 topic buses, service calls, and action servers, ensuring synchronous updates between physical devices and virtual models."
]

instance dt_technical_connection : DTDFVocab:TechnicalConnection [
